Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親一直在虐待我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得是從什麼時候開始的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被帶到他的工作室  是四歲時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後  一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天父親跟平時一樣來叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是該上藝術課了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個調查  居然花了半個月的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  每次都要你們陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.24,0:00:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸也拜託我了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我也閒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  文歌  為什麼要起訴…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.51,0:01:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於父親的事  我不自己動手的話就無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變了呢  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不得不改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我變了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧  美川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美川文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個美女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美川煌的女兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件滿天飛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還流傳到網上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.23,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虐待還是什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩說要我繼續匯報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還真是喜歡這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  好久沒在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次吧  上高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心哦  果然是來對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我向福音局申請回收你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這次又惹什麼禍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯認證碼  燒著了搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的搭檔倒像是完全失去了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千章？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到可以使文伽身份得到認可的判決實例
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.49,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最關鍵的文伽本人  卻已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天繼續跟蹤報道昨天的人氣作家美川煌虐待兒童事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其女提出起訴後剛好一周
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}美川煌  被親生女兒起訴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs20}森林裡的小夥伴們動畫化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說必須起訴父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心情一定難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是竟然任性地起訴父母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事實如何  對方可是親生父母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.98,0:05:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  法院居然洩漏了隱私的個人信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這更成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是在質問現代人洩漏他人隱私這一現狀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}女兒報復虐待自己的父親   請勿報道過度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您說兩句可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說兩句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您女兒現狀如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請對美川煌發表下您的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  用局長的名字  訂了一間房
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老師已經在房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在討論應付策略
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應付？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會上的責難和最佳銷售書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難把握兩者間的平衡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次用上次的方法行不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在那待命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.95,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  每次都約在我們學校門口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  為什麼你什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概  理由和你的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了接受  別無他法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡上的其實是美歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出來啦  這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才對文歌很溫柔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她體內的美歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本毫無關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野島要  我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}謝絕採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  你為什麼先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.01,0:08:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那時在神社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  好像聽到槍聲了  是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是你的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要自己干
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察那邊已經拜託過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的報紙和新聞會進行反省
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天才來了那麼多記者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿眼都是相機  麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再這樣我可受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白天又不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏香擔心的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕被拍照  採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是為啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為搭檔  有共同行動的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buon…giorno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}意大利語: 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…她住在意大利的哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我不擅長記片假名…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}日語中的外來語用片假名書寫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  見了面我直接問她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Buongiorno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽

Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛澤美麗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是海鷗市的野島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是警察吧  謝謝您的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也變漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我和那人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還會變得更漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗就是強大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快點變強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒  應該做得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我說完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生  那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那就這樣」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.86,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  我還想繼續保持女人的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想當什麼媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撫養費還是會給的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在電話裡已經說過了  對她來說  已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就不適合當母親啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼要生下我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.27,0:11:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要和父親結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一生中至少想體會一次所謂身為女人的喜悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚戒指啦  婚禮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜月  生孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚禮倒是可以再辦次  生小孩就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅廉佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「羅廉佐」…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了  文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為羅廉佐說今天想見我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小貓～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可愛的朋友～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.39,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是愛澤美麗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}她女兒也在耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是提出起訴的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs29}不就是煌的女兒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}是否通話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然對我表白  我也不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.38,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能去的地方應該不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再在附近找一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我也去找點線索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經藏不住煌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪名太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這本書會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煌老師的確應該贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作品…一字一句寫成的文章是無罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出版犯人的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出版社也托他的福  大賺了一筆不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此得到工資的我們  不也是同犯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葛西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊還在開會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也問過媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  果然是去了煌的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喜歡的文歌  已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的文歌不是美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事  有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子  對美歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是曾經最討厭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為我一直包容著小文的軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來  別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.09,0:15:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非小文你自己開槍…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後  小文只能靠你自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定一個人動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得努力不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小文又想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從要和夏香身邊逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從媽媽身邊逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒逃避呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界的人  不會這麼打你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美歌不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都推給我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那孩子向美歌開槍了 美歌才會消失的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於這種事  怎麼可能滿不在乎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭遇了不幸什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是自作自受…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  要去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是因為喜歡  或是討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的  小文你是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我鼓足了勇氣時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我能自己努力時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌來開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我這麼沒出息  你才出現的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝我開槍的話  兩個人都可以消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吧  美歌你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我？  明明是你自己想要朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子  騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你一直逃避著活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不想消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是因為喜歡或討厭  那是因為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文歌都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從二樓的陽台爬進來的  你也太不警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽還活著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三年來她一直和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後  我想過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然搞不懂人類生病之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是文伽一直和我在一起  是我的搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說什麼「不在了」這種沒出息的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽還活著  一定還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要擅自抹去她的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會撞到地上的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕時間在  你忍忍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得的  當然會記得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  兩個文歌都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我也想要朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想打籃球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人  學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有打工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想每天穿著校服上學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不是想和朋友一起去唱卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛肉火鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換郵箱地址
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著圍裙  做炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戲劇  開LIVE  然後是慶功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.41,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定可以實現的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死後文也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本無法寄出的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有些重要的話沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是本不該存在的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為不得不消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你創造出我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌  不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美歌最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文伽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣  就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯

Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fnDFLiSong-Bd\i1\bord0\fs24}{\fad(1100,1700)}死後文\N\N第十二話\N\N死後文

Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會去改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對  不會讓美歌和我融為一體的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡娜卡  0609
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解

